data.description: Wait no longer, this beautiful 4 bedroom, 3.5 bath townhome is available now. Located in the sought after Baxter Village community this home features hardwoods throughout the first floor, gas log fireplace and primary suite with tray ceilings. Upgraded Kitchen with refinished cabinets, newer appliances, and granite countertops. Great storage at lower level which could also be used as safe room. Easy access trail leading to Town Center which includes several restaurants, shops, library, fitness and more. Miles of walking/biking trails, 2 Community Centers, pools, tennis, several pocket parks, and award winning Fort Mill school district. Convenient access to I-77 and Uptown Charlotte.
